Artist Portfolio Website

Overview

This is a responsive artist portfolio website built using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap. It showcases an artist's work, including a hero section, a featured works carousel, and additional content pages.

Features

Responsive Design: Uses Bootstrap to ensure compatibility across devices.

Hero Section: A visually striking introduction with a background image overlay.

Navigation Bar: Fixed-top menu for easy access to different sections.

Image Carousel: A Bootstrap-powered slider to showcase featured artworks.

About & Contact Pages: Additional pages for artist information and contact details.

Custom Styles: Additional CSS for a unique and aesthetic design.

Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3

Bootstrap 5

Javascript

Setup Instructions

Clone the repository or download the project files.

git clone https://github.com/your-username/artist-portfolio.git

Navigate to the project folder.

cd artist-portfolio

Open index.html in a web browser.

File Structure

artist-portfolio/
│── index.html  (Main portfolio page)
│── about.html  (About page)
│── contact.html (Contact page)
│── styles.css  (Custom styles)
│── assets/     (Images and resources)
│── images/     (Artwork images)
└── README.md   (Project documentation)

Customization

Update styles.css to modify design elements.

Replace placeholder images in the images/ directory with your own artwork.

Modify text content in index.html, about.html, and contact.html as needed.

